EAGLE – Geospatial AI for Change Detection and ESG Intelligence

EAGLE is Neuralio’s Geospatial AI platform for automated analysis of multi-spectral, radar, and high-resolution satellite imagery. It performs:
•	Change detection and anomaly tracking for construction and land development;
•	Infrastructure and asset monitoring, detecting degradation, encroachment, and expansion in energy and transport networks;
•	Agricultural mapping for crop health, soil moisture, and yield forecasting;
•	Environmental assessment for ESG reporting and sustainability audits.
Through agentic GeoAI, EAGLE introduces reasoning agents capable of contextual inference and adaptive analysis — transforming static imagery into continuous operational intelligence. 
Added Value: EAGLE delivers high-frequency situational awareness, enabling stakeholders to monitor ESG indicators, optimize agricultural operations, and ensure regulatory compliance in real time.

SenCore – Real-Time Sensor and Data Fusion for Operational Insight

SenCore acts as the integration backbone connecting EO data with on-ground, airborne, and IoT sensor streams. Its event-driven architecture provides unified situational awareness for dynamic environments such as industrial facilities, construction zones, and renewable energy sites. It enables:
•	Predictive maintenance through continuous monitoring of energy infrastructure;
•	Construction progress verification via sensor-EO data fusion;
•	Real-time anomaly detection for environmental and operational events.
Added Value: SenCore transforms fragmented sensor networks into a single, coherent intelligence layer. It enhances data timeliness and reliability for infrastructure operators, regulators, and investors managing high-value physical assets.

TRANSITION – Predictive Modeling and Climate-Aware Decision Support

TRANSITION provides the AI modeling and digital-twin layer of Neuralio’s ecosystem. It uses multi-level agent-based simulations to project how environmental, economic, and policy factors interact under changing climate and market conditions. Key applications include:
•	Climate impact forecasting for renewable energy, agriculture, and infrastructure planning;
•	Land-use and resource optimization under variable climate and policy scenarios;
•	Spatial finance and ESG risk modeling, quantifying exposure to climate and operational risks at the asset level.
Added Value: TRANSITION turns EO and economic data into predictive foresight, supporting financial institutions, regulators, and planners in long-term sustainability and investment strategy design.

Integrated Value Proposition

Together, EAGLE, SenCore, and TRANSITION form a unified analytical ecosystem that operationalizes EO data into decision intelligence across key sectors:
•	ESG & Spatial Finance: Quantifying climate risk, carbon performance, and asset-level sustainability;
•	Infrastructure & Construction: Monitoring asset integrity, development progress, and compliance;
•	Renewable Energy: Identifying optimal solar and wind sites, forecasting yield, and reducing downtime;
•	Agriculture: Enhancing crop productivity through precision EO analytics;
•	Climate Resilience: Anticipating weather-driven disruptions and guiding adaptation planning;
•	Change Detection: Enabling continuous national-scale monitoring of land, energy, and environmental assets.
